{"tid":546580,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GiGi 忙 怕 戲　老 公 帶 女 接 收 工","createTime":"2018-01-31T15:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T07:26:39.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"516acb2fce414748ffe72606ae41cda5f875df3e","tid":546580,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:52:10.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）最近忙拍關錦鵬執導電影《八個女人一台戲》，大前日下午4時許在中環外景。當日下午茶休息時段，GiGi拿着三文治邊行邊食，不過發現被途人拿手機拍照，她醒目躲回劇組帳篷內休息，順便看play back。大約半小時後，劇組繼續開工，同場的商天娥因為身體不適，劇組安排車輛送她先走去看醫生。<br />\n<br />\nGiGi獨自多拍半小時，劇情交代她拿着紅酒沉思，似是滿懷心事，大約半小時便收工，GiGi到附近小店買公仔和賀卡即離開，然後上了七人車，原來是她的老公Sergio帶着囡囡來接GiGi放工，他們一家三口到金鐘太古廣場泊車，便到超市買東西，大約半小時後便回家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180130/large/30ec3p4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F30ec3p4e.jpg&h=6839490d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5390df5736dbcee6982fcad7a88f394a3f788f1f","tid":546580,"uid":96941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T07:09:43.000Z","msg":"西班牙籍老公Sergio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641ee967b99d4f650af31812b0b96639926181dd","tid":546580,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T07:17:46.000Z","msg":"好好勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602867c37024c59521ae609a27e34086af143aa9","tid":546580,"uid":168506,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T07:24:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84968010f50dab578613c495945d21d8d26be767","tid":546580,"uid":154596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"原來是她的西班牙籍老公Sergio帶着囡囡來接GiGi放工"}]}